 nešto kao da Bož traje

891
00:33:39,220 --> 00:33:40,480
 mjesec i po dana.

892
00:33:41,160 --> 00:33:42,120
 A s drugu stranu,

893
00:33:42,120 --> 00:33:45,300
 super da Uskrs je ostao ovako

894
00:33:45,300 --> 00:33:47,060
 kako je i priprema i korizma

895
00:33:47,060 --> 00:33:47,820
 zato što kažem

896
00:33:47,820 --> 00:33:49,040
 nije komercijaliziran

897
00:33:49,040 --> 00:33:51,220
 i nije se izgubila ona duhovna bit.

898
00:33:51,220 --> 00:33:52,940
 Znači mi imamo

899
00:33:52,940 --> 00:33:54,480
 najozbiljniju duhovnu pripremu.

900
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:54,940
 Gledajte,

901
00:33:54,940 --> 00:33:57,100
 mi križne puteve vodimo

902
00:33:57,100 --> 00:33:57,660
 po crkvama,

903
00:33:57,660 --> 00:33:58,460
 znači nema ljudi,

904
00:33:58,460 --> 00:34:00,040
 ali imamo križne puteve mladih,

905
00:34:00,040 --> 00:34:01,680
 pa to je ozbiljna priprema.

906
00:34:01,680 --> 00:34:03,480
 Razmišljanje o muci Kristovoj.

907
00:34:03,480 --> 00:34:03,960
 To je top.

908
00:34:04,340 --> 00:34:05,200
 i super da ga niko nije

909
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:06,020
 iskomercijalizirao.

910
00:34:06,020 --> 00:34:07,660
 Znači da su ljudi shvatili bit,

911
00:34:07,660 --> 00:34:08,780
 znači kroz korizmu,

912
00:34:08,780 --> 00:34:10,100
 odricanje od grijeha,

913
00:34:10,100 --> 00:34:11,320
 čižnjenje dobrih dijela,

914
00:34:11,320 --> 00:34:12,320
 molitva,

915
00:34:12,320 --> 00:34:13,700
 križni putevi

916
00:34:13,700 --> 00:34:15,020
 i naravno sada vrhunac

917
00:34:15,020 --> 00:34:15,640
 u ovome tjednu,

918
00:34:15,640 --> 00:34:16,220
 u velikome,

919
00:34:16,220 --> 00:34:17,780
 ispovjed.

920
00:34:17,780 --> 00:34:19,280
 To je, barim kod nas u Bazilici,

921
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:20,740
 rijeka ljudi koja se ispovjeda.

922
00:34:20,740 --> 00:34:21,980
 To je najbolja priprema.

923
00:34:21,980 --> 00:34:22,920
 Najbolja.

924
00:34:22,920 --> 00:34:23,780
 I zato govorim,

925
00:34:23,780 --> 00:34:24,320
 nekako mi je

926
00:34:24,320 --> 00:34:27,060
 od početka korizme

927
00:34:27,060 --> 00:34:27,840
 do Uskrsa

928
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:29,460
 traje jedna intenzivna,

929
00:34:29,600 --> 00:34:32,480
 40 dana priprema za Uskrs

930
00:34:32,480 --> 00:34:33,740
 koja nije narušena

931
00:34:33,740 --> 00:34:35,160
 najmo reći ovim svjetovnim duhom.

932
00:34:35,160 --> 00:34:36,880
 Koja je glavna poruka

933
00:34:36,880 --> 00:34:38,420
 ovog Uskrsa po vama?

934
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:40,440
 Za svakog od nas?

935
00:34:40,440 --> 00:34:41,320
 Uskrsni.

936
00:34:41,320 --> 00:34:43,340
 Znači Isu se uskrsne,

937
00:34:43,340 --> 00:34:44,500
 uskrsni i ti čovječe.

938
00:34:44,500 --> 00:34:45,480
 Uskrsni u duhu,

939
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:46,460
 uskrsni u srcu,

940
00:34:46,460 --> 00:34:48,060
 uskrsni u vjeru,

941
00:34:48,060 --> 00:34:48,540
 u nadi,

942
00:34:48,540 --> 00:34:49,800
 vjeruj ono,

943
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:50,600
 budi radostan,

944
00:34:50,600 --> 00:34:51,800
 živi punim plučima,

945
00:34:51,800 --> 00:34:54,660
 raduj se jer gospodin je živ,

946
00:34:54,660 --> 00:34:55,460
 nisi siročen,

947
00:34:55,460 --> 00:34:56,360
 nisi ostavljen,

948
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:57,920
 meni je to najljepše ono.

949
00:34:58,940 --> 00:35:00,720
 To bi ono poželio svima

950
00:35:00,720 --> 00:35:02,720
 jer kažem da i mi uskrsnemo

951
00:35:02,720 --> 00:35:03,960
 u duhu zajedno sa Isusom

952
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:06,200
 da osjetimo tu milost

953
00:35:06,200 --> 00:35:08,000
 i živu vjeru i nadu.

954
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:09,100
 To je najbolje.

955
00:35:09,100 --> 00:35:11,060
 Rekla sam,

956
00:35:11,060 --> 00:35:12,300
 Antunovski hodimate

957
00:35:12,300 --> 00:35:13,620
 u šestom mjesecu,

958
00:35:13,620 --> 00:35:15,380
 sedmog šestog,

959
00:35:15,380 --> 00:35:15,880
 je li tako?

960
00:35:15,880 --> 00:35:17,620
 To nije zapravo shodočešće,

961
00:35:17,620 --> 00:35:19,700
 nego kažu put vjere mladih.

962
00:35:19,700 --> 00:35:21,720
 Prošle godine je bio super,

963
00:35:21,720 --> 00:35:22,320
 odličan.

964
00:35:22,320 --> 00:35:23,600
 Koliko je ono bilo mladih ljudi?

965
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:25,260
 Ja mislim da je prošle godine

966
00:35:25,260 --> 00:35:26,900
 na završnici bilo oko 15.000,

967
00:35:26,900 --> 00:35:28,800
 ove godine čekujemo puno više.

968
00:35:28,940 --> 00:35:29,960
 Krenuli smo ozbiljno,

969
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:30,660
 imamo puno...

970
00:35:30,660 --> 00:35:31,460
 Za one koji ne znaju,

971
00:35:31,460 --> 00:35:32,280
 samo ćemo reći,

972
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:33,760
 krećete od...

973
00:35:33,760 --> 00:35:34,680
 Dakle, mi krećemo

974
00:35:34,680 --> 00:35:35,680
 od srskih sela,

975
00:35:35,680 --> 00:35:37,860
 pred programom u 11 sati,

976
00:35:37,860 --> 00:35:40,000
 zatim to je slavljenje

977
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:41,360
 i animiraju mladi.

978
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:42,780
 U 12 sati je Sveta Misa

979
00:35:42,780 --> 00:35:44,340
 i nakon Sveta Misa krećemo

980
00:35:44,340 --> 00:35:47,480
 prema drugom dijelu grada,

981
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:49,700
 to je konkretno našem svetištu

982
00:35:49,700 --> 00:35:50,560
 na Svetome Duhu,

983
00:35:50,560 --> 00:35:51,460
 Svetom Antunu.

984
00:35:51,460 --> 00:35:54,300
 Ali između toga imamo etape

985
00:35:54,300 --> 00:35:54,980
 gdje stajemo.

986
00:35:54,980 --> 00:35:56,340
 Prva je u Dubravi,

987
00:35:56,340 --> 00:35:57,560
 kod Heslagočkih fratara,

988
00:35:57,560 --> 00:35:58,780
 gdje ćemo imati molitvu,

989
00:35:58,780 --> 00:35:59,520
 okrepu

990
00:35:59,520 --> 00:36:02,140
 i onda idemo prema onom centralnom dijelu

991
00:36:02,140 --> 00:36:03,140
 gdje je evangelizacija

992
00:36:03,140 --> 00:36:03,780
 na trgu Bana Jelačića,

993
00:36:03,780 --> 00:36:07,040
 gdje će biti podignuta velika pozornica

994
00:36:07,040 --> 00:36:08,840
 i gdje će biti molitva,

995
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:09,580
 slavljenje,

996
00:36:09,580 --> 00:36:10,760
 jedan performans

997
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:13,940
 i tako evangelizacijskog karaktera.

998
00:36:13,940 --> 00:36:16,500
 Nakon trga krećemo dalje

999
00:36:16,500 --> 00:36:17,760
 naš put prema Bazilici

1000
00:36:17,760 --> 00:36:19,180
 gdje imamo klanjenje,

1001
00:36:19,180 --> 00:36:20,600
 slavljenje i druženje.

1002
00:36:20,600 --> 00:36:22,660
 Evo, to je ta nekakva ruta,

1003
00:36:22,660 --> 00:36:23,700
 ali ja uvijek govorim

1004
00:36:23,700 --> 00:36:25,860
 da ovo nije prazan hod.

1005
00:36:25,860 --> 00:36:28,300
 Mi već puno, puno vremena

1006
00:36:28,300 --> 00:36:29,720
 molimo za tu nakanu,

1007
00:36:29,720 --> 00:36:31,660
 pripremamo se što tehnički,

1008
00:36:31,660 --> 00:36:32,660
 što duhovno,

1009
00:36:32,660 --> 00:36:33,880
 jer nama je u interesu

1010
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:34,860
 da svi ljudi koji dožive

1011
00:36:34,860 --> 00:36:35,740
 zaista dođu,

1012
00:36:35,740 --> 00:36:37,020
 dožive duhovnu obnovu,

1013
00:36:37,040 --> 00:36:38,820
 dožive zajedništvo, ponos

1014
00:36:38,820 --> 00:36:40,740
 i to je ono što mladi najviše ističe.

1015
00:36:40,740 --> 00:36:41,860
 Mi ovi dana smo počeli

1016
00:36:41,860 --> 00:36:42,700
 na društvenim mrežama

1017
00:36:42,700 --> 00:36:45,220
 objavljivati isječke snimke

1018
00:36:45,220 --> 00:36:47,540
 zapravo sudionika

1019
00:36:47,540 --> 00:36:49,160
 prošlogodišnjih sahoda

1020
00:36:49,160 --> 00:36:50,680
 koji su dali svoje svjedočanstva

1021
00:36:50,680 --> 00:36:52,200
 kak je bilo

1022
00:36:52,200 --> 00:36:53,760
 i što su oni kako su to doživjeli.

1023
00:36:53,760 --> 00:36:55,420
 Tako da ljudi ovi sami mogu čuti

1024
00:36:55,420 --> 00:36:57,460
 što mogu očekivati

1025
00:36:57,460 --> 00:36:58,760
 ako dođu.

1026
00:36:58,760 --> 00:37:00,420
 Ja ovim putem pozivam svih,

1027
00:37:00,420 --> 00:37:02,460
 jer zaista sam ponosan

1028
00:37:02,460 --> 00:37:04,140
 da ovo više nije hrvatski,

1029
00:37:04,140 --> 00:37:04,940
 nije nacionalni.

1030
00:37:04,940 --> 00:37:06,820
 Prvo smo išli u okvirima Zagreba,

1031
00:37:06,820 --> 00:37:08,800
 pa smo iskočili iz toga na nacionalni.

1032
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:10,540
 Sad je internacionalni,

1033
00:37:10,540 --> 00:37:12,520
 jer nam dolaze sa svih strana,

1034
00:37:12,520 --> 00:37:13,620
 čak se uključuju, kažem,

1035
00:37:13,620 --> 00:37:14,920
 prošle godine je Bila i Makedonija,

1036
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:15,900
 i Bosna i Srbija,

1037
00:37:15,900 --> 00:37:19,280
 i ove susjedne zemlje Slovenija

1038
00:37:19,280 --> 00:37:20,140
 i ostali.

1039
00:37:20,140 --> 00:37:21,440
 Ali naši, naravno,

1040
00:37:21,440 --> 00:37:22,880
 Hrvati koji žive u dijaspori,

1041
00:37:22,880 --> 00:37:24,500
 dosta njih organizirano dolazi

1042
00:37:24,500 --> 00:37:26,340
 autobusima i to mi je nekako

1043
00:37:26,340 --> 00:37:27,420
 baš prekrasno vidjeti

1044
00:37:27,420 --> 00:37:30,220
 da će se okupiti ta naša mladež

1045
00:37:30,220 --> 00:37:31,600
 još jednom u Zagrebu,

1046
00:37:31,600 --> 00:37:33,540
 još jače, još više.

1047
00:37:33,540 --> 00:37:35,940
 I baš vidim jedan interes ogroman ko njih.

1048
00:37:35,940 --> 00:37:37,080
 A prekrasno je zapravo vidjeti

1049
00:37:37,080 --> 00:37:38,420
 mlade nasmijane ljude

1050
00:37:38,420 --> 00:37:39,880
 koji pjevaju i slave Boga.

1051
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:41,200
 E pa to je svjedočanstvo,

1052
00:37:41,200 --> 00:37:41,820
 to je radost,

1053
00:37:41,820 --> 00:37:42,660
 to je živi Bog.

1054
00:37:43,600 --> 00:37:45,620
 Zaplaćate li onda od sreće kad to...

1055
00:37:45,620 --> 00:37:47,300
 Naravno, da me emocije udare

1056
00:37:47,300 --> 00:37:49,080
 i da kad vidim što u mladosti...

1057
00:37:49,080 --> 00:37:50,420
 Dobri, jako organizator sam taj dan

1058
00:37:50,420 --> 00:37:51,220
 dosta pod šokom,

1059
00:37:51,220 --> 00:37:52,940
 ali me više dirne poslije

1060
00:37:52,940 --> 00:37:54,420
 kad gledam te snimke

1061
00:37:54,420 --> 00:37:55,540
 i to kad vidim kak je zapravo

1062
00:37:55,540 --> 00:37:56,300
 realno bilo.

1063
00:37:56,300 --> 00:37:57,320
 Ali se sjećam,

1064
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:58,220
 prošle godine je da je bilo

1065
00:37:58,220 --> 00:38:00,100
 dvirljivo kada smo na trgu

1066
00:38:00,100 --> 00:38:00,900
 imali molitvu,

1067
00:38:00,900 --> 00:38:01,840
 svi su kleklili

1068
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:03,300
 i je nastala ta tišina

1069
00:38:03,300 --> 00:38:04,420
 i kada je počela molitva.

1070
00:38:04,420 --> 00:38:05,280
 Bože, kako...

1071
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:06,380
 Ja mislim da nije bilo osobe

1072
00:38:06,380 --> 00:38:07,300
 koja tamo nije plakala.

1073
00:38:07,300 --> 00:38:08,660
 I onda kad smo ustali,

1074
00:38:13,600 --> 00:38:14,280
 sad naglašava ovo

1075
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:15,440
 da mi jako puno molimo

1076
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:16,920
 jer mi taj dan samo gledamo

1077
00:38:16,920 --> 00:38:17,860
 što smo molili.

1078
00:38:17,860 --> 00:38:19,800
 Dakle, nema taj dan više ništa,

1079
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:22,000
 nego taj dan se samo milost spušta.

1080
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:23,060
 Što smo nam molili,

1081
00:38:23,060 --> 00:38:23,860
 to se i događa.

1082
00:38:23,860 --> 00:38:26,000
 A kako se ta milost može

1083
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:28,140
 fra Stjepane na kraju spustiti

1084
00:38:28,140 --> 00:38:30,540
 na svakogodnost?

1085
00:38:30,540 --> 00:38:32,540
 Ne samo ova vaša sa hodučešća

1086
00:38:32,540 --> 00:38:34,160
 koja će biti ove godine

1087
00:38:34,160 --> 00:38:35,480
 7.6.

1088
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:37,340
 Dakle, svi se prijavite.

1089
00:38:37,340 --> 00:38:38,940
 I dalje tražite

1090
00:38:38,940 --> 00:38:41,740
 one bodyguardove, čuvare...

1091
00:38:41,740 --> 00:38:43,580
 Dakle, samo tražimo još bubnjare.

1092
00:38:43,600 --> 00:38:44,500
 Sve drugo imamo već.

1093
00:38:44,500 --> 00:38:45,020
 Ozbiljno?

1094
00:38:45,020 --> 00:38:46,400
 Ove godine ste puno brže.

1095
00:38:46,400 --> 00:38:50,100
 120 redara, 75 sestara prve pomoći.

1096
00:38:50,100 --> 00:38:52,600
 Dakle, svi drugi samo ako još bubnjara ima,

1097
00:38:52,600 --> 00:38:54,220
 to će nam dobro doći.

1098
00:38:54,220 --> 00:38:57,180
 Ok, to mi je prekrasno začuti.

1099
00:38:57,180 --> 00:38:59,720
 Dakle, na kraju, milost Božju,

1100
00:38:59,720 --> 00:39:02,180
 kako spustiti na nas,

1101
00:39:02,180 --> 00:39:04,060
 na pojedinca, na naše obitelji,

1102
00:39:04,060 --> 00:39:05,860
 na našu domovinu, na svijet?

1103
00:39:05,860 --> 00:39:07,700
 Nismo pričali da li može,

1104
00:39:07,700 --> 00:39:10,100
 ali kad mi postavljaš pitanje

1105
00:39:10,100 --> 00:39:11,500
 kako spustiti, pa molitvom.

1106
00:39:11,500 --> 00:39:14,460
 pa ja bi se onda pomolio za vas

1107
00:39:14,460 --> 00:39:15,760
 i za one koji će gledati ovaj video.

1108
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:16,560
 Ko će molim?

1109
00:39:16,560 --> 00:39:17,080
 Može.

1110
00:39:17,080 --> 00:39:20,780
 Dobri Bože,

1111
00:39:20,780 --> 00:39:23,200
 hvala ti na ovom trenutku milosti.

1112
00:39:23,200 --> 00:39:25,640
 Hvala ti na daru svake osobe

1113
00:39:25,640 --> 00:39:27,700
 što si je stvorio tako kakva jest.

1114
00:39:28,800 --> 00:39:29,700
 Molim te, gospodine,

1115
00:39:29,700 --> 00:39:31,600
 ti si nas iz ljubavi stvorio

1116
00:39:31,600 --> 00:39:33,360
 i postavio ovaj svijet.

1117
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:35,720
 Nekoga da bude svečenik,

1118
00:39:35,720 --> 00:39:37,520
 nekoga majka, otac, dijete.

1119
00:39:37,520 --> 00:39:39,940
 Blagoslovi nas Isuse snagom

1120
00:39:39,940 --> 00:39:40,780
 duha svetoga,

1121
00:39:40,780 --> 00:39:42,140
 ti koji si ju skrsnuo.

1122
00:39:42,140 --> 00:39:44,100
 Neka vatra duha svetoga

1123
00:39:44,100 --> 00:39:45,040
 siđe i na nas.

1124
00:39:45,040 --> 00:39:46,960
 Neka mać duha svetoga

1125
00:39:46,960 --> 00:39:48,740
 odagna od nas svaku tjeskobu,

1126
00:39:48,740 --> 00:39:50,580
 strah, sumnju, depresiju,

1127
00:39:50,580 --> 00:39:52,060
 svaku krizu.

1128
00:39:52,860 --> 00:39:53,920
 Milošću duha svetoga

1129
00:39:53,920 --> 00:39:55,340
 odmnovi naše obitelji.

1130
00:39:55,340 --> 00:39:57,580
 Neka zavlada mir, ljubav.

1131
00:39:57,580 --> 00:39:59,140
 Molimo te, Isuse,

1132
00:39:59,140 --> 00:40:01,120
 svojom ljubavlju izliječi

1133
00:40:01,120 --> 00:40:02,000
 sve naše rane,

1134
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:04,360
 rane koje smo nanijeli jedni drugima.

1135
00:40:04,360 --> 00:40:06,040
 Izliječi, gospodine,

1136
00:40:06,040 --> 00:40:07,540
 naše međuljudske odnose.

1137
00:40:07,540 --> 00:40:09,280
 Daruj nam duh ljubavi.

1138
00:40:09,280 --> 00:40:10,920
 Ljubavi da možemo ljubiti

1139
00:40:10,920 --> 00:40:12,020
 i svoje neprijatelje.

1140
00:40:12,020 --> 00:40:14,380
 Dođi, duše Isusa Hrista,

1141
00:40:14,380 --> 00:40:15,860
 ti koji si mir,

1142
00:40:15,860 --> 00:40:16,980
